    Abstract EvaluableExpressionVisitor offering a convenient interface. All visit methods redirect the call to visitOther(EvaluableExpression). Implementors can thus override only certain visit overloads and handle all other cases in visitOther(EvaluableExpression). If the implementor want visitOther(de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.evaluableexpressions.EvaluableExpression) to be called for expressions he overrode the visit method, he can call the matching overload of super.visit.
